Nc3
{ This move was analyzed by Greco; White gambits the e4-pawn.  7.Bd2!?  and  7.Nbd2!?  are interesting continuations. }
7... Nxe4 { Black should take the central pawn! } 8. O-O Bxc3
{ The most precise! } 9. d5
