10... b5 { Black forces White's bishop to leave a good diagonal. } 11. Bb3
{ After  11.Bd3  Ne6∓  , White's passive pieces are not enough for the pawn. }
11... a5
{ Black is ready to play ...a4, while White is struggling to come up with a move. }
