6. dxc6 Nxc6 { Black develops the knight towards the center. } 7. d4 Bd6
{ It's always nice to develop and protect at the same time. } 8. O-O O-O 9. c3
{ White builds a nice pawn chain, but the c1-bishop and the b1-knight are still not developed. }
9... Bg4
{ Black has finished development and stands a bit better. The game may continue with  10.Nbd2  Qd7  , Black connects the rooks  11.a4  Rfe8  , getting the free open file.  12.h3  Bh5  , let's keep the pin alive.  13.b4?  is not a good move but what else to do?  13...Re3!  The rook is a monster on e3.  14.Bb2  Ne7⩱  and the knight  will go to d5, with a dream position for Black. }
