{ White creates a nice pawn chain, but the c1-bishop is still unhappy. } 10...
Re8 { A simple move to grab the open file. } 11. Nc4 Bc7
{ Let's not trade this bishop. Black is already better, but let me show you how easily White can get into trouble with natural developing moves. }
12. Bd2 { A normal move, White develops a piece, you may say. But... } 12...
Ne4
