6. Qxe4 { White falls for our trap! } 6... a4
{ And just like that White's bishop has no good squares. } 7. Bxa4
{ White now loses a piece by force in all lines. } 7... Nf6
{ Now we start harassing the enemy queen and force it to lose connection with the bishop. }
8. Qf4
{ 8.Qb4  e5  9.Qh4  g5-+  , @@StartFEN@@rnbqkb1r/1p2pp1p/2p2np1/8/B3Q3/8/PPPP1PPP/RNB1K1NR w KQkq - 1 8@@EndFEN@@  8.Qh4  g5-+  , @@StartFEN@@rnbqkb1r/1p2pp1p/2p2np1/8/B3Q3/8/PPPP1PPP/RNB1K1NR w KQkq - 1 8@@EndFEN@@  8.Qc4  b5-+  . }
8... g5 9. Qb4 e5 10. Qb3 b5
