13. Nf3 Bxf3 14. Bxf3 O-O
{ Believe it or not, but with equal material the engine already gives Black a winning edge @@StartBracket@@-2.74@@EndBracket@@ since White's king is just too weak. }
15. O-O Qe5 16. a3 Bd6
{ Now White wishes the g-pawn would still be around to guard the king. The game is over. }
